133
00:08:55,553 --> 00:08:59,596
[SPEAKER_09]: Um, in that you share some details about the actual, um,

134
00:09:02,113 --> 00:09:11,357
[SPEAKER_09]: intended position of the parking space, its size, some details about the curb cut that would expand, and so on.

135
00:09:12,337 --> 00:09:16,299
[SPEAKER_09]: Would either of you like to share any details about that?

136
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:18,560
[SPEAKER_15]: Certainly.

137
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:29,424
[SPEAKER_15]: One of the nice things about this is he's adding a parking space, which is going to cut down on street congestion.

138
00:09:31,558 --> 00:09:38,760
[SPEAKER_15]: And it actually benefits the public good because the space that would be lost on the street isn't really even a full space.

139
