[SPEAKER_15]: It's about eight and a half feet.

140
00:09:40,921 --> 00:09:47,042
[SPEAKER_15]: So it certainly benefits the public good to have less on street congestion.

141
00:09:47,883 --> 00:09:53,364
[SPEAKER_15]: And especially on a clog street where people getting in and out of driveways can be very difficult by its own right.

142
00:09:54,404 --> 00:10:00,546
[SPEAKER_15]: And it certainly benefits in that aspect as well as reducing the nonconformity

143
00:10:01,223 --> 00:10:05,466
[SPEAKER_15]: that currently exists at the property, where it only has the two spaces rather than the four.

144
00:10:06,967 --> 00:10:12,211
