157
00:11:54,469 --> 00:12:02,155
[SPEAKER_15]: So again, not to be repetitive, it will certainly help cut down on existing congestion on the street, which is,

158
00:12:02,665 --> 00:12:05,727
[SPEAKER_15]: obviously something that benefits the community at large.

159
00:12:11,810 --> 00:12:12,150
[SPEAKER_09]: Okay.

160
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:19,934
[SPEAKER_09]: And then, so I just want to make sure we're clear on the relief being sought here.

161
00:12:20,094 --> 00:12:31,020
[SPEAKER_09]: So in terms of the permit refusal, part of it is that the off street parking space is in the front yard.

162
00:12:32,078 --> 00:12:36,840
[SPEAKER_09]: of the building, which is not allowed.

163
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:48,684
[SPEAKER_09]: And then the other relief, if I understood correctly from the application, is that the dimensions of the parking space are slightly smaller than what's allowed.

164
00:12:48,724 --> 00:12:49,184
[SPEAKER_09]: Is that right?

165
00:12:50,284 --> 00:12:51,145
[SPEAKER_15]: That is correct.

