1288
02:01:45,601 --> 02:01:59,306
[SPEAKER_22]: I think that having three separate units actually serves to reduce that versus having a larger property with multiple bedrooms and rooms that are undesignated as either a kitchen or a dining room.

1289
02:01:59,826 --> 02:02:01,787
[SPEAKER_22]: And I'll leave it at that.

1290
02:02:03,227 --> 02:02:05,928
