1304
02:03:29,977 --> 02:03:39,821
[SPEAKER_08]: Well one is that since this is an apart in the apartment one district it does seem to me that the, the intention is aligned with Medford existing zoning.

1305
02:03:42,003 --> 02:03:58,990
