1366
02:11:13,224 --> 02:11:20,768
[SPEAKER_08]: And I recognize what the Smiths are saying in terms of why is this a particular hardship over other ones.

1367
02:11:20,868 --> 02:11:33,894
[SPEAKER_08]: But I would say that this is a very common situation in historic communities, where I think by the very fact that you're inheriting these buildings on these particular lots that were

1368
