[SPEAKER_09]: And the variance is only required here if it creates a new nonconformity.

1412
02:17:05,610 --> 02:17:11,135
[SPEAKER_09]: So yeah, the standard is not substantially more detrimental to the neighborhood.

1413
02:17:13,917 --> 02:17:18,882
