1417
02:17:42,245 --> 02:17:44,327
[SPEAKER_08]: So it's already nonconforming.

1418
02:17:44,387 --> 02:17:50,891
[SPEAKER_08]: I don't see additional detriment since the building itself is not changing.

1419
02:17:53,592 --> 02:17:54,052
[SPEAKER_08]: I agree.

1420
02:17:58,475 --> 02:17:59,256
[SPEAKER_09]: Yeah.

