1423
02:18:07,247 --> 02:18:08,428
[SPEAKER_09]: But I don't.

1424
02:18:09,089 --> 02:18:20,498
[SPEAKER_09]: So I want to acknowledge the possibility that for some multifamilies, you know, maybe the the side yard should be different.

1425
02:18:20,578 --> 02:18:24,381
[SPEAKER_09]: But but here, yeah, they've stayed true to the building footprint.

1426
02:18:24,501 --> 02:18:31,447
